subproject.description: The project is expected to have reactivation of livelihoods that was affected by the Tsunami and support to strategic recovery planning and enhanced disaster risk management system. It also aims to increase disaster risk awareness programs to be conducted by stakeholders both at national and community level.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: Tonga Tsunami Early Recovery
